ABOUT PROJECT

1) In this project ,we will show how to
create “Desktop Notifier” using python.
2) A desktop notifier is a simple
application which produces a notification
message in form of a pop up message on
desktop.
3) This application works for any kind of
operating system like windows, Linux or
MAC.
4) It is advanced technology which
helps in notifying important events in
our day to day life.
5) A notifier window pops out on
desktop screen which helps us to remind
the important work which has to be done.

